{{Function |origin = LU |summary = Returns an array of forms sorted by an array of [[Form_Type_IDs|type code]] integers. JIP NVSE Plugin v40 merged Lutana NVSE plugin v19. '''As of JIPv40, This function's syntax was changed from Lutana v19, requiring that you pass the arrays via their IDs (set to integers) if you use the script compiler override (CO).''' |name = SortFormsByType |returnType = array |arguments = {{FunctionArgument |Name = formsArrayID |Type = array }}{{FunctionArgument |Name = typesArrayID |Type = array }}
== Example == array_var arrForms array_var arrTypes array_var arrSorted
let arrSorted := SortFormsByType arrForms, arrTypes
== Example with CO == array_var arrForms array_var arrTypes array_var arrSorted int iFormsArrayID int iTypesArrayID ... set iFormsArrayID to arrForms set iTypesArrayID to arrTypes let arrSorted := SortFormsByType iFormsArrayID iTypesArrayID
== Old Syntax (Lutana standalone) == (arrSorted) SortFormsByType arrForms:array arrTypes:array
}} ==See Also== [[Form_Type_IDs]] [[Category:Functions_(JIP)]] [[Category:Miscellaneous_Functions_(JIP)]] [[Category:Array_Functions]]

